{"tid":507141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免費體驗靈性雙修？技師吹氣挑逗嚇壞按摩男","createTime":"2017-12-23T02:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T03:57:31.000Z","uid":156968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64d50d6150107d45793c848e7ac1eb0db5a92c33","tid":507141,"uid":156968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"浙江寧波有男子用一張按摩店388元人民幣優惠劵消費，沒想到女技師竟突然在他耳邊吹氣出手挑逗，嚇得他馬上叫停。然而優惠券寫有「免費體驗靈性雙修」字樣，店家辯稱只是將服務項目名稱寫得較露骨。<br />\n<br />\n小袁（化名）周一收到按摩店家素問道的抵用券，宣傳店內獨家推出的養生項目，而他近日坐辦公室感到疲累，決定前往消費放鬆一下。但他沒注意到傳單不但有引人遐想的宣傳照，正面是一位女性按摩師將手放在上身赤裸的男客人身上，背面則是一名身穿黑絲襪的女生伸出美腿「輕踩」在男客人上身，上面還有「憑此劵免費體驗靈性雙修」字樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171222_PN_MASSAGE_02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171222_PN_MASSAGE_02.png&h=30edc324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171222_PN_MASSAGE_03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171222_PN_MASSAGE_03.png&h=fc47c3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小袁到了這家店後，要辦會員卡才能按摩，且店員補充說明「這次的服務是送的，不收費」，所以他辦了一張會員卡並繳交7500元人民幣。他進一步提到，當時他被帶到一個小房間內，洗完澡後就從背部開始按摩，但後來女按摩師就開始對他亂來：「我就不情願，然後就跟經理說我不想做了，我要退卡。」事後店家回應，會員卡一旦啟用，便不能退款。<br />\n<br />\n隔日，小袁帶著當地記者再度回到店家，等半個多小時後，經理才出面交涉。經理表示，小袁日前收到的優惠券確實是店裡，但圖片僅供參考：「泡麵上面寫的有牛肉，那裡面有牛肉嗎？那只是廣告而已」，而「靈性雙修」是指臉部護理的項目，只是取名較為露骨，並強調店內只做正規按摩，否認小袁所講的詳情，但小袁隨後被帶到別的樓層，並退他6500元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2693831/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2693831%2F&d=%2F%2B5%2Bqc2hEJKMc6pdDVG3I%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=32f5f991\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2693831/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dae4de3596561e333390ad0fea0c42c376d0fb8","tid":507141,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"嗚呀"},{"pid":"41c03e88ce8d93be8ffa9889f22f870442d8a833","tid":507141,"uid":14135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"貨不對辦<br />\n我指條女"},{"pid":"08558239933a32b5ed5335d656f70fc3fbb75c4e","tid":507141,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貨不對辦<br />\n我指條女</blockquote><br />\n如果靚女，點會搞咁多野"},{"pid":"f7a9d92165679f2022256e23b902a03d2517cadb","tid":507141,"uid":69794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:53:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HoHQNbGfRDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHoHQNbGfRDs&d=%2F%2B5%2Bqc2hEJKMc6pdDVG3I%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=af6fe3fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HoHQNbGfRDs</a>"},{"pid":"c51d899c9bbed5d3835f752b539a495954196d3b","tid":507141,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:57:31.000Z","msg":"屌 gay test?"}]}